      "t_start": 117.0,
      "estimated_duration_s": 14.0,
      "narration_text": "A team deploys a three-qubit code and sees logical error rates three times higher than expected. Investigation: their ancilla measures both parity stabilizers sequentially. One ancilla error spreads to two data qubits. They add a second ancilla \u2014 one per stabilizer. Logical error rates fall to predicted levels. The fix costs one extra qubit.",
